<p>Hello <%%= @actor.respond_to?(:email) ? @actor.email : "there" %>,</p>

<p>
  <%%= @manager_actor.present? ? @manager_actor.email : "Someone" %>
  granted you <strong><%%= @role.humanize.downcase %></strong> access.
</p>

<%% if @access_url.present? %>
  <p><a href="<%%= @access_url %>">Open the shared item</a></p>
<%% end %>
